Your role, your impact
This job posting is available in English only due to the location of publication.
As an Oracle Cloud HCM Techo-Functional Conversion Consultant, you’ll play a key role in helping clients transition from legacy systems to the full Oracle HCM suite. Your expertise will ensure smooth data conversion and successful implementations that make a real difference for our clients.
Travel to client sites is required up to 25% of the time.
