Provide Oracle HCM offshore techno-functional consulting services;
Coordinate with functional leads to convert client data for all HCM modules and to create Fast Formulas as per the scope of the project;
Monitor conversion statistics and issues;
Develop and test Fast Formulas.
Keys to your success
